[[File:Warbot2.jpg|thumb|right|150px|Full-length view of a warbot]]
'''Warbots''' were [[Assassin droid/Legends|assassin]] [[Battle droid/Legends|battle droids]] used by [[Mercenary/Legends|mercenaries]] during the days of the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]].<ref name="KOTOR 2">''[[Star Wars: Knights of the Old Republic II: The Sith Lords]]''</ref>

==History==
The [[Meetra Surik|Jedi Exile]] encountered two warbots on [[Telos IV]]. A wily [[Twi'lek/Legends|Twi'lek]] [[Gender/Legends|female]] mercenary commander attempted to trap her by stationing herself and two of her warbots, as well as a minefield with around 6 minor fragmentation mines, in front of the Jedi Exile as the [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] charged towards the abandoned [[Czerka Arms/Legends|Czerka]] base in [[RZ-0031]]. As with the other unfortunate mercenaries, the [[Twi'lek/Legends|Twi'lek]] was slain, and her two warbots were destroyed.<ref name="KOTOR 2" />

